ActParliament of Canada Act
SubjectBoard of Internal Economy - Appointments of the Hon. Peter Van Loan and the Hon. Gordon O'Connor
PrecisOrder (a) terminating the appointments made by Order in Council P.C. 2010-1066 of August 6, 2010, and (b) appointing the Honourable PETER VAN LOAN and the Honourable GORDON O'CONNOR to be members of the Board of Internal Economy of the House of Commons.
